data.description: 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms home in Tortosa!!. New paint and new carpet!. Plenty of space in this large 3,165 sq ft home!. It has a family room and a living room. Open kitchen with upgraded cabinets. All bedrooms are upstairs. Extremely large master bedroom with an unusually large master closet. Upstairs laundry for your convenience. Full length covered patio. With its 2. 5 car garage, you have storage, without losing parking stalls!! .Just down the street from an elementary school!. Park and Disc Golf course nearby.
